<h1><a id="welcome" class="heading_anchor" href="#welcome" aria-hidden="true">#</a>Welcome</h1>
<p>The 18th annual Libre Graphics Meeting (LGM) will be held in Nuremberg, Germany on May 28-31, 2025.</p>
<p>The Libre Graphics Meeting  is an annual meeting on Free/Libre and
Open Source software for graphics.</p>
<h2><a id="key-actions" class="heading_anchor" href="#key-actions" aria-hidden="true">#</a>Key Actions</h2>
<ol>
<li>Read our <a href="/2025/program">Program</a>,</li>
<li>
<ul>
<li>if you plan to attend, please <a href="/2025/register">Register!</a> yourself,</li>
<li>otherwise, <a href="/2025/news/2025-03-29_0001-video-streaming-and-recording/">a live broadcast and recordings will be available</a>, monitor this site for further directions,</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>and consider to <a href="/2025/donate">Donate!</a>.</li>
</ol>
