<h2><a id="special-focus--reimagination" class="heading_anchor" href="#special-focus--reimagination" aria-hidden="true">#</a>Special focus – RE:imagination</h2>
<p>The Libre Graphics Meeting faced significant challenges during and after
the pandemic. In <a href="/2024">Rennes</a>, France, 2024, the local organization team revitalized
the event, and now we aim to rebuild the international community and
strengthen the structures around the Libre Graphics Meeting.</p>
<p>Join us to reconnect with old friends and forge new connections. Under the
theme of <a href="/2025/program/label-re-imagination/">RE:imagination</a>,
we are going to explore the future of the Libre Graphics Meeting together.</p>

